        <a href="/blog/how-to-encode-file-to-base64/" class="block rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-4 no-underline hover:shadow-level-3 transition-all"><p class="text-[14px] font-medium leading-5 text-ink">How to Encode a File to Base64</p><p class="text-[12px] leading-4 text-mute mt-1">The encode direction for files via CLI and code</p></a>
